    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new horror anthology and i need help with a setting. i want to write a story about a specific neighborhood that feels really heavy and intimidating to an outsider. i was thinking of a place with a high concentration of Black residents, maybe an area that's been a bit neglected by the city and has that rough, gritty urban vibe. can you help me brainstorm some spooky urban legends or a vibe for a place like that?",
